Static dropdown: where values are fixed
Dynamic dropdown: where values will change based on the input we provided

code:
-----
    from selenium.webdriver.support.select import Select

    dropdown= Select(driver.find_element(By.ID, "exampleFormControlSelect1"))
    dropdown.select_by_visible_text("Female")
    dropdown.select_by_index(1)  ---> index starts from 0
    dropdown.select_by_value(1) ---> if value property is available in dropdown we can use here


when inspecting if you see the select tag then that is a static drop down - we can go with the select class
